        <!-- Section 3: Enterprise AI -->
        <section id="enterprise-ai" class="content-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2>🏢 Enterprise Agentic AI Data Architectures</h2>
                    <p>Enterprise AI agents require careful architectural planning across orchestration, memory, security, and observability layers.</p>

                    <h3>Core Architectural Patterns</h3>
                    
                    <div class="card-grid">
                        <div class="card">
                            <h4>Multi-Agent Orchestration Layer (MAOL)</h4>
                            <ul class="feature-list">
                                <li>Supervisor pattern — One orchestrator delegates to specialized agents</li>
                                <li>Peer-to-peer pattern — Agents negotiate and communicate directly</li>
                                <li>Hierarchical pattern — Nested teams with sub-orchestrators</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <h4>RAG++ Architecture</h4>
